{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"9d5ee761-5c07-4798-9a11-aeea7c22ce72","content":"The directory appears empty, so I'll answer based on my knowledge of .NET MAUI APIs:\n\n**`ios:Page.UseSafeArea=\"True\"`** — This is **outdated**. It was a Xamarin.Forms API. In .NET MAUI, the correct approach is to use padding that respects safe areas, or use the built-in behavior where `ContentPage` already respects safe areas by default on iOS.\n\n**`IgnoreSafeArea=\"True\"`** — This **does not exist** as a property in .NET MAUI. It was a Xamarin.Forms concept.\n\n### What to do in .NET MAUI (.NET 10):\n\n1. **Safe area insets are respected by default** — `ContentPage` content is automatically laid out within safe areas on iOS.\n\n2. **To extend content into unsafe areas** (e.g., a background image behind the notch), use platform-specific code or set negative margins/padding, or use `Page.IgnoreSafeArea`:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns:ios=\"clr-namespace:Microsoft.Maui.Controls.PlatformConfiguration.iOSSpecific;\n             assembly=Microsoft.Maui.Controls\"\n             ios:Page.UseSafeArea=\"False\">\n```\n\n   Setting `UseSafeArea=\"False\"` lets content extend behind the notch/home indicator.\n\n3. **For a background image that fills the full screen** while keeping other content safe:\n\n```xml\n<Grid>\n    <Image Source=\"background.png\" Aspect=\"AspectFill\" />\n    <Grid Padding=\"{OnPlatform iOS='20,60,20,20'}\">\n        <!-- Your safe content here -->\n    </Grid>\n</Grid>\n```\n\n### Summary\n\n| Tutorial claim | Reality in .NET MAUI |\n|---|---|\n| `ios:Page.UseSafeArea=\"True\"` | Exists but `True` is already the default — you only need it if toggling back on |\n| `IgnoreSafeArea=\"True\"` on Grid | **Does not exist** — use layout techniques instead |\n\nThe tutorial likely targets Xamarin.Forms. In MAUI, safe areas are handled by default and you only intervene with `ios:Page.UseSafeArea=\"False\"` when you want to opt *out*.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"a099a47b-f1da-4f57-a6e3-87f2946a4faa","outputTokens":546,"requestId":"9428:2A1132:13C6D39:162889E:6A066F90"},"id":"8ab7a5c5-de98-4413-82a2-c00a0118b8f6","timestamp":"2026-05-15T00:58:05.591Z","parentId":"cc8dd110-27b4-4297-80b5-6b2c07e8cb0c"}
